\">GREAT<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/winock\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d604aa085cae88b5ff5733231fbd059b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d604aa085cae88b5ff5733231fbd059b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/winock\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Patrick Horemans <small>(Winock)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 22, 2018<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">A must have!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">A must have<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/butchewing\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/b99763b481d66859ede644bb41a6a00a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/b99763b481d66859ede644bb41a6a00a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/butchewing\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">butchewing<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 25, 2018<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">I really enjoy the features and flexibility that this plugin offers.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent.. has many tweaks,<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/open5g\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/7e405a0898d5d4e6e2b061bd626d025f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/7e405a0898d5d4e6e2b061bd626d025f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/open5g\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">open5g<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 26, 2017<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">I was having a problem with WP posts list page - the title column would crunch down to just a few characters wide when using an SEO plugin which added columns.  I posted on the SEO Framework support site then, minutes later, just happened to try Admin Tweaks. One of the many tweaks is one to adjust the Post page Title column width using pixels or percent. \n\nThere are too many other tweaks to mention them.  Some may seem trivial, such as adjusting the color for different stages of posts that I find useful.\n\nAdmin Tweaks rolls up many individual plugins and scripts into just one.  I have yet to use it much so I can't judge if there are bugs or performance hits.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice admin plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/synopsisconcept\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/41b5a847ec3ed2acb5af028f04906e05?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/41b5a847ec3ed2acb5af028f04906e05?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/synopsisconcept\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">synopsisconcept<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 24, 2017<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Works on the last WP Version. Nice for a quick tweak of admin dashboards and else. \nFonctionne sur les derni\u00e8res versions de WP. Pratique pour le tweak rapide du cot\u00e9 admin du tableau de bord.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simply awesome!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/aguseo\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/57554805e57d21c1036c8b91f944c8ca?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/57554805e57d21c1036c8b91f944c8ca?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/aguseo\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Andras Guseo <small>(aguseo)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 24, 2017<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">This is a really cool plugin helping my everyday work in the admin dashboard. I install it for all my sites. I love it!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fantastic<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/bigjake36\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9aebcd12aa6535c144d6fff936858c5e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9aebcd12aa6535c144d6fff936858c5e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/bigjake36\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bigjake36<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 3, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><p>This plugin works for version 4.3 of WP and it's fantastic !!!<\/p>\n<p>It does everything and more!! So, if your looking to change the admin look of your admin panel and more this is the plugin that's a must have.<\/p>\n<p>Great Job !!!\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
    },
    "short_description": "With Admin Tweaks you&#039;ll be able to simplify and make deep customizations in the administrative interface.",
    "description": "<p>With Admin Tweaks you&#8217;ll be able to simplify and make <strong>deep customizations<\/strong> in the administrative interface.<br \/>\nIt&#8217;s a compilation of hooks for enhancing, styling and reducing WordPress backend.<\/p>\n<p>Do you like to adjust and style the backend as much as the frontend?<br \/>\nSo, we are together!<\/p>\n<h4>Main Features<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Admin Bar: remove, add and modify menu items.<\/li>\n<li>Admin Menus: remove menu and submenu items; sort Settings menu; rename &#8220;Posts&#8221;.<\/li>\n<li>Appearance: hide general elements; create admin notices.<\/li>\n<li>Dashboard: remove and add widgets.<\/li>\n<li>General Settings: enable arcane Link Manager; privacy; other misc options.<\/li>\n<li>Listings: customize rows and columns for post types, users and plugins.<\/li>\n<li>Media: custom columns; re-attachment; sanitize filenames; jpeg quality; audio\/photo\/video metadata.<\/li>\n<li>Plugins: many row modifications; live filter by keyword\/active\/inactive; move plugins menus from the main menu into the Tools menu (Code Snippets, ACF, The SEO Framework, Hide Admin Notices).<\/li>\n<li>User Profile: remove almost everything; add custom CSS.<\/li>\n<li>Login: redirects; errors; modify almost everything; add custom CSS.<\/li>\n<li>Maintenance Mode: with minimum Role allowed and possibility to block only the backend.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Acknowledgments<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Everything changed after <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.stackexchange.com\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WordPress Stack Exchange<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Plugin interface using @bainternet&#8217;s <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/bainternet\/Admin-Page-Class\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Admin Page Class<\/a><\/li>\n<li>CSS for hiding help texts adapted from <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/plugins\/admin-expert-mode\/\" rel=\"ugc\">Admin Expert Mode<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Everything started with <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/plugins\/adminimize\/\" rel=\"ugc\">Adminimize<\/a>, by Frank B\u00fceltge, which does an awesome job hiding WordPress elements, but I wanted more, and these are some of the great resources where I found many snippets: <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.stackexchange.com\/questions\/1567\/best-collection-of-code-for-your-functions-php-file\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Stack Exchange<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/wpengineer.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WPengineer<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wpbeginner.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">wpbeginner<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/css-tricks.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">CSS-TRICKS<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/wp.smashingmagazine.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Smashing Magazine<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/justintadlock.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Justin Tadlock<\/a>&#8230;<\/li>\n<li>The option to hide the help texts from many areas of WordPress uses the CSS file of the plugin <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/plugins\/admin-expert-mode\/\" rel=\"ugc\">Admin Expert Mode<\/a>, by Scott Reilly.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
